{"tid":1254403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"621事後感受 & 理性討論","createTime":"2019-06-24T06:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T15:54:21.000Z","uid":134133,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8eafa0f8a196fd9dc7dc167a33a2dbf1e6cae3c5","tid":1254403,"uid":134133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:08:19.000Z","msg":"呢兩日發夢聽到身邊好多fd都有相同感受 <br />\n想討論一下個夢 點樣可以改善做得更好<br />\n<br />\n我覺得罷工唔緊要<br />\n但你一定冇可能expect人漫長咁無限罷工<br />\n我都差唔多兩個星期冇返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以其實趁多人出黎既時候 大家係唔係應該做啲野<br />\n而唔係反而叫人散, 聽日再黎過....</span></span><br />\n<br />\n621吹到咁大... <br />\n上晒頭版又話deadline<br />\n又話行動升級<br />\n又話不回應不散.. <br />\n最尾呢? 叫人返屋企休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我係政府/一哥 我都唔驚你啦<br />\n下次更加唔會理你地 照板煮碗<br />\n反正你地自己會走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">622 623係星期六日 大部份人放假<br />\n點解唔好好利用 叫在場人留/退守政總呢?<br />\n另外, 黎緊再有呢啲行動<br />\n係唔係可以諗多一步<br />\n如果再係冇人出黎回應/冇結果既話<br />\n我地下一步係點 而唔係到時先算 叫人返屋企先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n好坦白講 <br />\n愈拖一定會愈黎愈少人出 <br />\n一黎體力影響 真係好攰<br />\n二黎已經請到冇晒假<br />\n同埋香港人真係好善忘... 慢慢個心情就會屌淡左<br />\n所以一定要把握每次機會<br />\n<br />\n有人話621成功咗<br />\n成功令班狗士氣低咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但請記住 我地唔係要呢啲<br />\n我地要既4大訴求 1個都仲未回應! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外請連登仔唔好再得把口 ! !<br />\n叫人唔好分化 自己就係咁分化<br />\n同你意見唔同就比你屌係鬼 係5毛...<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武唔好再屌和理 <br />\n和理都請唔好再阻止勇武<br />\n其實大家都係想香港好啲姐</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 夢入面已經用晒全部AL+SL, 冇得再罷, 但所有行動放工都會john"},{"pid":"a9435ccce2cef653adfcba0aeab104a894b916ff","tid":1254403,"uid":134133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:15:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"895ea900143eac8ef38b4b806d7ae9a4a84d5edf","tid":1254403,"uid":134133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:20:24.000Z","msg":"今日出唔到黎既巴打 <br />\n626星期三記得要出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a433d626f72414882d9a103ae216fcb6716b7511","tid":1254403,"uid":134133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:41:42.000Z","msg":"推 多啲人睇到"},{"pid":"82fe4e74715a888a81027685aca0fe301341e17d","tid":1254403,"uid":134133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T06:53:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wz56b7f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwz56b7f.png&h=e2b9afc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n招集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01dd60eb5d1fade33d2fe5e648e59a45b0bf59e2","tid":1254403,"uid":134133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T07:25:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"339101a365e4e63e2fbbbc2a19b8b05ed14adead","tid":1254403,"uid":134133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:26:19.000Z","msg":"見到身邊啲人開始慢慢冇左件事 大家唔好放棄呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8047a2c0fe4c3cc6678c0c4976f210adcbaff676","tid":1254403,"uid":67477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:28:08.000Z","msg":"其實大家都等緊626<br />\n有無諗過621係迴音箱"},{"pid":"7af932231219b6456c0253e522db00782a0f3b6a","tid":1254403,"uid":134133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8047a2c0fe4c3cc6678c0c4976f210adcbaff676","tid":1254403,"uid":67477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:28:08.000Z","msg":"其實大家都等緊626<br />\n有無諗過621係迴音箱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:29:17.000Z","msg":"咁咩叫DEADLINE?"},{"pid":"